TI  - Species composition and niche characteristics of secondary plant communities on regenerated landslides af- ter earthquake
ST  - 地震滑坡体自然恢复后次生植物群落物种组成及生态位特征
PY  - 2022
T2  - Chinese Journal of Ecology
VL  - 41
