TI  - A comparative geological, tectonic and geomorphological assessment of the Charlotte, Regent and Madina landslides, Western area, Sierra Leone
PY  - 2021
T2  - Geoenvironmental Disasters
VL  - 8
IS  - 1
C7  - 16
