TI  - Periglacial vegetation dynamics in Arctic Russia: Decadal analysis of tundra regeneration on landslides with time series satellite imagery
PY  - 2020
T2  - Environmental Research Letters
VL  - 15
IS  - 10
C7  - 105020
DO  - 10.1088/1748-9326/abb500
