TI  - NAOTURAL REGENERATION AND ARTIFICIAL THINNING FOR EARLY FOREST RESTORATION ON A PERMANENTLY CLOSED SKI SLOPE
PY  - 2021
T2  - International Journal of GEOMATE
VL  - 20
