TI  - Using the NDVI and mean shift segmentation to extract landslide areas in the Lioukuei experimental forest region with multi-temporal FORMOSAT-2 images
PY  - 2017
T2  - Taiwan Journal of Forest Science
VL  - 32
IS  - 3
