TI  - Species diversity variation of Cupressus funebris secondary forest in landslide site after 5.12 Wenchuan Earthquake
PY  - 2018
T2  - Chinese Journal of Applied and Environmental Biology
VL  - 24
IS  - 6
SP  - 1404
