AD  - Biological Laboratory, Sapporo Campus, Hokkaido University of Education, Sapporo 002-8072, 5-3-1 Ainosato, Kita-ku, Japan
AD  - Forest Ecology and Diversity Group, Hokkaido Research Centre, Forestry and Forest Products Research Institute, Sapporo 062-8516, 7 Hitsujigaoka, Toyohira-ku, Japan
