TI  - Loss of a dominant nitrogen-fixing shrub in primary succession: Consequences for plant and below ground communities
PY  - 2012
T2  - Journal of Ecology
VL  - 100
IS  - 5
SP  - 1074
EP  - 1084
DO  - 10.1111/j.1365-2745.2012.02000.x
