TI  - Vegetation recovery on landslides of the Wenchuan earthquake and its influencing factors: A case study in Longxi-Hongkou Nature Reserve
PY  - 2014
T2  - Chinese Journal of Applied and Environmental Biology
VL  - 20
IS  - 3
