TI  - Evaluation of vegetation and soil characteristics during slope vegetation recovery procedure
PY  - 2013
T2  - Nongye Gongcheng Xuebao/Transactions of the Chinese Society of Agricultural Engineering
VL  - 29
IS  - 3
SP  - 124
EP  - 131
