AD  - Institute for Tropical Ecosystem Studies, University of Puerto Rico, San Juan, 00931, P.O. Box 21910, Puerto Rico
AD  - Department of Botany, University of Hawaii at Manoa, Honolulu, HI 96822, 3190 Maile Way, United States
AD  - Department of Forestry and Watershed Management, Humboldt State University, Arcata, CA 95521, 1 Harpst Street, United States
